            "text": "and do you take to you castles, haply to dwell forever?",
            "numberInSurah": 129,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 372,
            "ruku": 322,
            "hizbQuarter": 149,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3062,
            "text": "When you assault, you assault like tyrants!",
            "numberInSurah": 130,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 372,
            "ruku": 322,
            "hizbQuarter": 149,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3063,
            "text": "So fear you God, and obey you me;",
            "numberInSurah": 131,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 372,
            "ruku": 322,
            "hizbQuarter": 149,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3064,
            "text": "and fear Him who has succoured you with what you know,",
            "numberInSurah": 132,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 372,
            "ruku": 322,
            "hizbQuarter": 149,
            "sajda": false
          },
