            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 372,
            "ruku": 322,
            "hizbQuarter": 149,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3068,
            "text": "They said, 'Alike it is to us, whether thou admonishest, or art not one of the admonishers;",
            "numberInSurah": 136,
            "juz": 19,
            "manzil": 5,
            "page": 372,
            "ruku": 322,
            "hizbQuarter": 149,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 3069,
            "text": "this is nothing but the habit of the ancients,",
