            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 574,
            "ruku": 508,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5490,
            "text": "Surely We have sent unto you a Messenger as a witness over you, even as We sent to Pharaoh a Messenger,",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 574,
            "ruku": 508,
            "hizbQuarter": 229,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5491,
            "text": "but Pharaoh rebelled against the Messenger, so We seized him remorselessly.",
