          },
          {
            "number": 5561,
            "text": "upon that day man shall say, 'Whither to flee?'",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5562,
            "text": "No indeed; not a refuge!",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5563,
            "text": "Upon that day the recourse shall be to thy Lord.",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5564,
            "text": "Upon that day man shall be told his former deeds and his latter;",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5565,
            "text": "nay, man shall be a clear proof against himself,",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5566,
            "text": "even though he offer his excuses.",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5567,
            "text": "Move not thy tongue with it to hasten it;",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5568,
            "text": "Ours it is to gather it, and to recite it.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5569,
            "text": "So, when We recite it, follow thou its recitation.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5570,
            "text": "Then Ours it is to explain it.",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 577,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5571,
            "text": "No indeed; but you love the hasty world,",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5572,
            "text": "and leave be the Hereafter.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5573,
            "text": "Upon that day faces shall be radiant,",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5574,
            "text": "gazing upon their Lord;",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5575,
            "text": "and upon that day faces shall be scowling,",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5576,
            "text": "thou mightest think the Calamity has been wreaked on them.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5577,
            "text": "No indeed; when it reaches the clavicles",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5578,
            "text": "and it is said, 'Who is an enchanter?'",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5579,
            "text": "and he thinks that it is the parting",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5580,
            "text": "and leg is intertwined with leg,",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5581,
            "text": "upon that day unto thy Lord shall be the driving.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 512,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5582,
            "text": "For he confirmed it not, and did not pray,",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5583,
            "text": "but he cried it lies, and he turned away,",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5584,
            "text": "then he went to his household arrogantly.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5585,
            "text": "Nearer to thee and nearer",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5586,
            "text": "then nearer to thee and nearer!",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5587,
            "text": "What, does man reckon he shall be left to roam at will?",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5588,
            "text": "Was he not a sperm-drop spilled?",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5589,
            "text": "Then he was a blood-clot, and He created and formed,",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5590,
            "text": "and He made of him two kinds, male and female.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5591,
            "text": "What, is He not able to quicken the dead?",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 513,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 76,
        "name": "سُورَةُ الإِنسَانِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Insaan",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Man",
        "revelationType": "Medinan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5592,
            "text": "Has there come on man a while of time when he was a thing unremembered?",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5593,
            "text": "We created man of a sperm-drop, a mingling, and We made him hearing, seeing.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5594,
            "text": "Surely We guided him upon the way whether he be thankful or unthankful.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5595,
            "text": "Surely We have prepared for the unbelievers chains, fetters, and a Blaze.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5596,
            "text": "Surely the pious shall drink of a cup whose mixture is camphor,",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 578,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5597,
            "text": "a fountain whereat drink the servants of God, making it to gush forth plenteously.",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5598,
            "text": "They fulfil their vows, and fear a day whose evil is upon the wing;",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5599,
            "text": "they give food, for the love of Him, to the needy, the orphan, the captive:",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5600,
            "text": "'We feed you only for the Face of God; we desire no recompense from you, no thankfulness;",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5601,
            "text": "for we fear from our Lord a frowning day, inauspicious.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5602,
            "text": "So God has guarded them from the evil of that day, and has procured them radiancy and gladness,",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5603,
            "text": "and recompensed them for their patience with a Garden, and silk;",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5604,
            "text": "therein they shall recline upon couches, therein they shall see neither sun nor bitter cold;",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5605,
            "text": "near them shall be its shades, and its clusters hung meekly down,",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5606,
            "text": "and there shall be passed around them vessels of silver, and goblets of crystal,",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5607,
            "text": "crystal of silver that they have measured -- very exactly.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5608,
            "text": "And therein they shall be given to drink a cup whose mixture is ginger,",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5609,
            "text": "therein a fountain whose name is called Salsabil.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 231,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5610,
            "text": "Immortal youths shall go about them; when thou seest them, thou supposest them scattered pearls,",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5611,
            "text": "when thou seest them then thou seest bliss and a great kingdom.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5612,
            "text": "Upon them shall be green garments of silk and brocade; they are adorned with bracelets of silver, and their Lord shall give them to drink a pure draught.",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5613,
            "text": "Behold, this is a recompense for you, and your striving is thanked.'",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 514,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5614,
            "text": "Surely We have sent down the Koran on thee, a sending down;",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5615,
            "text": "so be thou patient under the judgment of thy Lord, and obey not one of them, sinner or unbeliever.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5616,
            "text": "And remember the Name of thy Lord at dawn and in the evening",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 579,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5617,
            "text": "and part of the night; bow down before Him and magnify Him through the long night.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5618,
            "text": "Surely these men love the hasty world, and leave be behind them a heavy day.",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5619,
            "text": "We created them, and We strengthened their joints; and, when We will, We shall exchange their likes.",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5620,
            "text": "Surely this is a Reminder; so he who will, takes unto his Lord a way.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5621,
            "text": "But you will not unless God wills; surely God is ever All-knowing, All-wise.",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5622,
            "text": "For He admits into His mercy whomsoever He will; as for the evildoers, He has prepared for them a painful chastisement.",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 515,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 77,
        "name": "سُورَةُ المُرۡسَلَاتِ",
        "englishName": "Al-Mursalaat",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Emissaries",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5623,
            "text": "By the loosed ones successively",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5624,
            "text": "storming tempestuously",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5625,
            "text": "by the scatterers scattering",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5626,
            "text": "and the severally severing",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5627,
            "text": "and those hurling a reminder",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5628,
            "text": "excusing or warning,",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5629,
            "text": "surely that which you are promised is about to fall!",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5630,
            "text": "When the stars shall be extinguished,",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5631,
            "text": "when heaven shall be split",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5632,
            "text": "when the mountains shall be scattered",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5633,
            "text": "and when the Messengers' time is set,",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5634,
            "text": "to what day shall they be delayed?",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5635,
            "text": "To the Day of Decision.",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5636,
            "text": "And what shall teach thee what is the Day of Decision?",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5637,
            "text": "Woe that day unto those who cry it lies!",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5638,
            "text": "Did We not destroy the ancients,",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5639,
            "text": "and then follow them with the later folk?",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5640,
            "text": "So We serve the sinners.",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5641,
            "text": "Woe that day unto those who cry it lies!",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 580,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5642,
            "text": "Did We not create you of a mean water,",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5643,
            "text": "that We laid within a sure lodging",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5644,
            "text": "till a known term decreed?",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5645,
            "text": "We determined; excellent determiners are We.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5646,
            "text": "Woe that day unto those who cry it lies!",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5647,
            "text": "Made We not the earth to be a housing",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5648,
            "text": "for the living and for the dead?",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5649,
            "text": "Set We not therein soaring mountains? Sated you with sweetest water?",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5650,
            "text": "Woe that day unto those who cry it lies!",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5651,
            "text": "Depart to that you cried was lies!",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5652,
            "text": "Depart to a triple-massing shadow",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5653,
            "text": "unshading against the blazing flame",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5654,
            "text": "that shoots sparks like dry faggots,",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5655,
            "text": "sparks like to golden herds.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5656,
            "text": "Woe that day unto those who cry it lies!",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5657,
            "text": "This is the day they shall not speak",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5658,
            "text": "neither be given leave, and excuse themselves.",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5659,
            "text": "Woe that day unto those who cry it lies!",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5660,
            "text": "'This is the Day of Decision; We have joined you with the ancients;",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5661,
            "text": "if you have a trick, try you now to trick Me!'",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5662,
            "text": "Woe that day unto those who cry it lies!",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 516,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5663,
            "text": "Truly the godfearing shall dwell amid shades and fountains,",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 517,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5664,
            "text": "and such fruits as their hearts desire:",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 517,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5665,
            "text": "'Eat and drink, with wholesome appetite, for that you were working.'",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 517,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5666,
            "text": "Even so do We recompense the good-doers.",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 517,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5667,
            "text": "Woe that day unto those who cry it lies!",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 517,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5668,
            "text": "'Eat and take your joy a little; you are sinners!'",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 517,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5669,
            "text": "Woe that day unto those who cry it lies!",
            "numberInSurah": 47,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 517,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5670,
            "text": "When it is said to them, 'Prostrate yourselves!' they prostrate not.",
            "numberInSurah": 48,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 517,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5671,
            "text": "Woe that day unto those who cry it lies!",
            "numberInSurah": 49,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 517,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5672,
            "text": "In what discourse after this will they believe?",
            "numberInSurah": 50,
            "juz": 29,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 581,
            "ruku": 517,
            "hizbQuarter": 232,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 78,
        "name": "سُورَةُ النَّبَإِ",
        "englishName": "An-Naba",
        "englishNameTranslation": "The Announcement",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5673,
            "text": "Of what do they question one another?",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5674,
            "text": "Of the mighty tiding",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5675,
            "text": "whereon they are at variance.",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5676,
            "text": "No indeed; they shall soon know!",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5677,
            "text": "Again, no indeed; they shall soon know!",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5678,
            "text": "Have We not made the earth as a cradle",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5679,
            "text": "and the mountains as pegs?",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5680,
            "text": "And We created you in pairs,",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5681,
            "text": "and We appointed your sleep for a rest;",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5682,
            "text": "and We appointed night for a garment,",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5683,
            "text": "and We appointed day for a livelihood.",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5684,
            "text": "And We have built above you seven strong ones,",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5685,
            "text": "and We appointed a blazing lamp",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5686,
            "text": "and have sent down out of the rainclouds water cascading",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5687,
            "text": "that We may bring forth thereby grain and plants,",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5688,
            "text": "and gardens luxuriant.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5689,
            "text": "Surely the Day of Decision is an appointed time,",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5690,
            "text": "the day the Trumpet is blown, and you shall come in troops,",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5691,
            "text": "and heaven is opened, and become gates,",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5692,
            "text": "and the mountains are set in motion, and become a vapour.",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5693,
            "text": "Behold, Gehenna has become an ambush,",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5694,
            "text": "for the insolent a resort,",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5695,
            "text": "therein to tarry for ages,",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5696,
            "text": "tasting therein neither coolness nor any drink",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5697,
            "text": "save boiling water and pus",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5698,
            "text": "for a suitable recompense.",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5699,
            "text": "They indeed hoped not for a reckoning,",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5700,
            "text": "and they cried loud lies to Our signs;",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5701,
            "text": "and everything We have numbered in a Book.",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5702,
            "text": "'Taste! We shall increase you not save in chastisement.'",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 582,
            "ruku": 518,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5703,
            "text": "Surely for the godfearing awaits a place of security,",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 519,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5704,
            "text": "gardens and vineyards",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 519,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5705,
            "text": "and maidens with swelling breasts, like of age,",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 519,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5706,
            "text": "and a cup overflowing.",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 519,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5707,
            "text": "Therein they shall hear no idle talk, no cry of lies,",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 519,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5708,
            "text": "for a recompense from thy Lord, a gift, a reckoning,",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 519,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5709,
            "text": "Lord of the heavens and earth, and all that between them is, the All-merciful of whom they have no power to speak.",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 519,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5710,
            "text": "Upon the day when the Spirit and the angels stand in ranks they shall speak not, save him to whom the All-merciful has given leave, and who speaks aright.",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 519,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5711,
            "text": "That is the true day; so whosoever wills takes unto his Lord a resort.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 519,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5712,
            "text": "Lo, We have warned you of a nigh chastisement, upon the day when a man shall behold what his hands have forwarded, and the unbeliever shall say, 'O would that I were dust!'",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
