      },
      {
        "number": 79,
        "name": "سُورَةُ النَّازِعَاتِ",
        "englishName": "An-Naazi'aat",
        "englishNameTranslation": "Those who drag forth",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5713,
            "text": "By those that pluck out vehemently",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5714,
            "text": "and those that draw out violently,",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5715,
            "text": "by those that swim serenely",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5716,
            "text": "and those that outstrip suddenly",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5717,
            "text": "by those that direct an affair!",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5718,
            "text": "Upon the day when the first blast shivers",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5719,
            "text": "and the second blast follows it,",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5720,
            "text": "hearts upon that day shall be athrob",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5721,
            "text": "and their eyes shall be humbled.",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5722,
            "text": "They shall say, 'What, are we being restored as we were before?",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5723,
            "text": "What, when we are bones old and wasted?'",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5724,
            "text": "They shall say, 'That then were a losing return!'",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5725,
            "text": "But it shall be only a single scare,",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5726,
            "text": "and behold, they are awakened.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5727,
            "text": "Hast thou received the story of Moses?",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 583,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5728,
            "text": "When his Lord called to him in the holy valley, Towa:",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5729,
            "text": "'Go to Pharaoh; he has waxed insolent.",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5730,
            "text": "And say, 'Hast thou the will to purify thyself;",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5731,
            "text": "and that I should guide thee to thy Lord, then thou shalt fear?''",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5732,
            "text": "So he showed him the great sign,",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5733,
            "text": "but he cried lies, and rebelled,",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5734,
            "text": "then he turned away hastily,",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5735,
            "text": "then he mustered",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5736,
            "text": "and proclaimed, and he said, 'I am your Lord, the Most High!'",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5737,
            "text": "So God seized him with the chastisement of the Last World and the First.",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5738,
            "text": "Surely in that is a lesson for him who fears!",
            "numberInSurah": 26,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 520,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5739,
            "text": "What, are you stronger in constitution or the heaven He built?",
            "numberInSurah": 27,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5740,
            "text": "He lifted up its vault, and levelled it,",
            "numberInSurah": 28,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5741,
            "text": "and darkened its night, and brought forth its forenoon;",
            "numberInSurah": 29,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5742,
            "text": "and the earth-after that He spread it out,",
            "numberInSurah": 30,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5743,
            "text": "therefrom brought forth its waters and its pastures,",
            "numberInSurah": 31,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5744,
            "text": "and the mountains He set firm,",
            "numberInSurah": 32,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5745,
            "text": "an enjoyment for you and your flocks.",
            "numberInSurah": 33,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5746,
            "text": "Then, when the Great Catastrophe comes",
            "numberInSurah": 34,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5747,
            "text": "upon the day when man shall remember what he has striven,",
            "numberInSurah": 35,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5748,
            "text": "and Hell is advanced for whoever sees,",
            "numberInSurah": 36,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5749,
            "text": "then as for him who was insolent",
            "numberInSurah": 37,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5750,
            "text": "and preferred the present life,",
            "numberInSurah": 38,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5751,
            "text": "surely Hell shall be the refuge.",
            "numberInSurah": 39,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5752,
            "text": "But as for him who feared the Station of his Lord and forbade the soul its caprice,",
            "numberInSurah": 40,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5753,
            "text": "surely Paradise shall be the refuge.",
            "numberInSurah": 41,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5754,
            "text": "They will question thee concerning the Hour, when it shall berth.",
            "numberInSurah": 42,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5755,
            "text": "What art thou about, to mention it?",
            "numberInSurah": 43,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5756,
            "text": "Unto thy Lord is the final end of it.",
            "numberInSurah": 44,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5757,
            "text": "Thou art only the warner of him who fears it.",
            "numberInSurah": 45,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5758,
            "text": "It shall be as if; on the day they see it, they have but tarried for an evening, or its forenoon.",
            "numberInSurah": 46,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 584,
            "ruku": 521,
            "hizbQuarter": 233,
            "sajda": false
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "number": 80,
        "name": "سُورَةُ عَبَسَ",
        "englishName": "Abasa",
        "englishNameTranslation": "He frowned",
        "revelationType": "Meccan",
        "ayahs": [
          {
            "number": 5759,
            "text": "He frowned and turned away",
            "numberInSurah": 1,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5760,
            "text": "that the blind man came to him.",
            "numberInSurah": 2,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5761,
            "text": "And what should teach thee? Perchance he would cleanse him,",
            "numberInSurah": 3,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5762,
            "text": "or yet remember, and the Reminder profit him.",
            "numberInSurah": 4,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5763,
            "text": "But the self-sufficient,",
            "numberInSurah": 5,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5764,
            "text": "to him thou attendest",
            "numberInSurah": 6,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5765,
            "text": "though it is not thy concern, if he does not cleanse himself.",
            "numberInSurah": 7,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5766,
            "text": "And he who comes to thee eagerly",
            "numberInSurah": 8,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5767,
            "text": "and fearfully,",
            "numberInSurah": 9,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5768,
            "text": "to him thou payest no heed.",
            "numberInSurah": 10,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5769,
            "text": "No indeed; it is a Reminder",
            "numberInSurah": 11,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5770,
            "text": "(and whoso wills, shall remember it)",
            "numberInSurah": 12,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5771,
            "text": "upon pages high-honoured,",
            "numberInSurah": 13,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5772,
            "text": "uplifted, purified,",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5773,
            "text": "by the hands of scribes",
            "numberInSurah": 15,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5774,
            "text": "noble, pious.",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5775,
            "text": "Perish Man! How unthankful he is!",
            "numberInSurah": 17,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5776,
            "text": "Of what did He create him?",
            "numberInSurah": 18,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5777,
            "text": "Of a sperm-drop He created him, and determined him,",
            "numberInSurah": 19,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5778,
            "text": "then the way eased for him,",
            "numberInSurah": 20,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5779,
            "text": "then makes him to die, and buries him,",
            "numberInSurah": 21,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5780,
            "text": "then, when He wills, He raises him.",
            "numberInSurah": 22,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5781,
            "text": "No indeed! Man has not accomplished His bidding.",
            "numberInSurah": 23,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5782,
            "text": "Let Man consider his nourishment.",
            "numberInSurah": 24,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5783,
            "text": "We poured out the rains abundantly,",
            "numberInSurah": 25,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 585,
            "ruku": 522,
            "hizbQuarter": 234,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 5784,
