            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6007,
            "text": "surely thy Lord is ever on the watch.",
            "numberInSurah": 14,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6008,
            "text": "As for man, whenever his Lord tries him, and honours him, and blesses him, then he says, 'My Lord has honoured me.'",
