            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6009,
            "text": "But when he tries him and stints for him his provision, then he says, 'My Lord has despised me.'",
            "numberInSurah": 16,
            "juz": 30,
            "manzil": 7,
            "page": 593,
            "ruku": 531,
            "hizbQuarter": 237,
            "sajda": false
          },
          {
            "number": 6010,
            "text": "No indeed; but you honour not the orphan,",
